[section#reentrancy
    [:en] Reentrancy
    [:zh_CN] 可重入性
]

[para]
[:en]
Except where explicitly specified in this standard, it is [%@impldef which
functions in Standard C++ library may be recursively reentered]
implementation-defined which functions in the Standard [=Cpp] library may be
recursively reentered.
[:zh_CN]
除非在本标准中明确说明，标准 [=Cpp] 程序库中的哪些函数可以递归地重入是
[%@impldef 标准 C++ 程序库中的哪些函数可以递归地重入]由实现定义的。
